          "order": 1,
          "content": {
            "headline": "Our Story",
            "subheadline": "Dedicated to cleaner, healthier spaces since 2010",
            "backgroundImage": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/4021256/pexels-photo-4021256.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1920"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "text-story",
          "type": "text",
          "title": "Our Mission",
          "isActive": true,
          "order": 2,
          "content": {
            "text": "<h3>Our Mission</h3><p>At Sparkle Clean, we believe everyone deserves a clean, healthy living and working environment. Founded in 2010, we've grown from a small family business to a trusted cleaning service provider serving hundreds of homes and businesses.</p><p>Our commitment to using only eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products ensures the safety of your family, pets, and employees while delivering exceptional results. Every member of our team undergoes rigorous training and background checks because we understand that trust is earned.</p><p>We're not just cleaning spaces – we're creating healthier environments where people can thrive.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "team-1",
          "type": "team",
          "title": "Our Cleaners",
          "isActive": true,
          "order": 3,
          "content": {
            "title": "Meet Our Cleaning Experts",
            "subtitle": "Professional, friendly, and dedicated to excellence",
            "members": [
              {
                "name": "Sarah Johnson",
                "role": "Founder & CEO",
                "bio": "Sarah started Sparkle Clean in 2010 with a mission to provide eco-friendly cleaning services. She oversees operations and ensures quality standards."
              },
              {
                "name": "Michael Torres",
                "role": "Operations Manager",
                "bio": "Michael manages our team of 50+ cleaners and ensures every job meets our high standards. He specializes in commercial cleaning operations."
              },
              {
                "name": "Lisa Wong",
                "role": "Training Director",
                "bio": "Lisa develops our training programs and certifies all new team members in our eco-friendly cleaning protocols and safety standards."
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
